{"title":"国旗升起的时候","authors":["杨德祥"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":10,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"国旗升起的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨德祥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国旗升起的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个人都会自觉停留！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随着一个庄严昂首。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了心中的日出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了眼前的锦绣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们曾赴汤蹈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改写春秋！啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有倒下才有屹立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有摧枯拉朽才有绿肥红瘦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升旗的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见中国挥手告别落后！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国旗升起的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个人都会精神抖擞！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的激情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟随着一个信念伴奏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了梦里的蓝图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了壮丽的追求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们曾斩关夺隘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造辉煌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，有牺牲才有新生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有扬眉吐气才有天长地久。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升旗的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见中国挺胸走向富有！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}